article.title: Pirate Fanart
article.rawContent:
Fanart of **Pirate**, a character of [Pirateaba](https://thewanderinginn.fandom.com/wiki/Pirateaba).

## The Creation of Pirate

[![The Creation of Pirate](/img/posts/pirate-fanart/the-creation-of-pirate-pirateaba-small.png)](/img/posts/pirate-fanart/the-creation-of-pirate-pirateaba.png)

Made using [Easy Pose](https://store.steampowered.com/app/979710/Easy_Pose/) and [Adobe Photoshop](https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html). Finished on **2021-09-21**.

## Unlimited Bread: Words

[![Unlimited Bread: Words](/img/posts/pirate-fanart/unlimited-bread-words-small.png)](/img/posts/pirate-fanart/unlimited-bread-words.png)

Made using [Easy Pose](https://store.steampowered.com/app/979710/Easy_Pose/) and [Adobe Photoshop](https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html). Finished on **2021-10-05**.
